+//!
+//! These tests launch the `pi` binary in a tmux session, drive scripted
+//! interactions, capture pane output, and emit JSONL artifacts for CI diffing.
+//!
+//! Run:
+//! ```bash
+//! cargo test --test e2e_tui_features
+//! ```
